			e aumentar seus lucros.
		</p>

		<div class=" flex flex-col px-4 sm:px-0 sm:grid sm:w-fit mx-auto mt-10 grid-cols-2 gap-4  justify-center items-center place-items-center place-content-center place-self-center justify-items-center ">
			<div class=" w-full sm:w-96 h-32 rounded-3xl  border-primary border  bg-[#181200] ">
			</div>
			<div class=" w-full sm:w-96 h-32 rounded-3xl  border-primary border  bg-[#181200] ">
			</div>
			<div class=" w-full sm:w-96 h-32 rounded-3xl  border-primary border  bg-[#181200] ">
			</div>
			<div class=" w-full sm:w-96 h-32 rounded-3xl  border-primary border  bg-[#181200] ">
			</div>
		</div>

	</section>



	<section class=" flex sm:flex-row flex-col justify-center gap-5 sm:gap-24 mt-24 sm:px-0 px-10">
