	</section>


	<section class=" mt-20 sm:mt-0">
		<h5 class=" text-3xl underline text-primary text-center font-bold">O Que você vai Receber</h5>
		<div class=" flex flex-col px-4 sm:px-0 sm:grid sm:w-fit mx-auto mt-10 grid-cols-2 gap-4  justify-center items-center place-items-center place-content-center place-self-center justify-items-center ">
			<div class=" sm:w-[500px]  w-full  h-32 rounded-3xl  border-primary border  bg-[#181200] relative  justify-center items-center flex px-10 ">
				<p class=" text-2xl">Acesso exclusivo a fornecedores confiáveis.</p>
				<div class=" sm:size-16 size-12 flex justify-center items-center text-4xl font-bold rounded-3xl bg-primary  text-black  absolute -bottom-5 -right-2">
					<span>1</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class=" sm:w-[500px]  w-full  h-32 rounded-3xl  border-primary border  bg-[#181200] relative  justify-center items-center flex px-10 ">
				<p class=" text-2xl">Método testado que vai te ensinar a economizar dinheiro.</p>
				<div class=" sm:size-16 size-12 flex justify-center items-center text-4xl font-bold rounded-3xl bg-primary  text-black  absolute -bottom-5 -right-2">
					<span>2</span>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class=" sm:w-[500px]  w-full  h-32 rounded-3xl  border-primary border  bg-[#181200] relative  justify-center items-center flex px-10 ">
